I have a question to ask you.

26
00:02:12,946 --> 00:02:14,197
Me? What is it?

27
00:02:15,114 --> 00:02:18,660
When Yoo Jae-beom
entered Korea at Incheon Airport,

28
00:02:18,743 --> 00:02:21,204
