-This number…
-Yes.

32
00:02:39,722 --> 00:02:41,891
Located in Seocho-dong, Seocho-gu, Seoul,

33
00:02:41,975 --> 00:02:44,519
at Seoul Central District Court's
Criminal Division,

34
00:02:45,353 --> 00:02:46,938
it's Chief Judge Kang Da-wit's office.

35
00:02:47,563 --> 00:02:49,107
That's your number, right?

36
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:50,733
What are you talking about?

37
00:02:51,234 --> 00:02:54,404
Why would I talk on the phone
with that punk? I've never called…

38
00:02:55,905 --> 00:02:58,366
Your classmate
from elementary school called.

39
00:03:01,661 --> 00:03:03,287
"Kim Ju-seop"? Who's that?

40
00:03:03,371 --> 00:03:05,873
-He said "Juvenile" would ring a bell.
-Juvenile?

41
00:03:07,083 --> 00:03:09,002
Right. Kim Juvenile.

42
00:03:11,713 --> 00:03:14,090
What? Did you remember something?

43
00:03:18,594 --> 00:03:19,804
Good morning!

44
00:03:20,388 --> 00:03:23,349
