We as attorneys support LGBTQIA+ rights.

212
00:11:47,228 --> 00:11:48,687
Please sign our petition!

213
00:11:48,771 --> 00:11:50,272
-Please sign.
-We'd appreciate it!

214
00:11:50,356 --> 00:11:52,775
Let's make a world without discrimination.

215
00:11:52,858 --> 00:11:54,360
Yeah. Please sign.

216
00:11:54,443 --> 00:11:57,905
If you donate and complete our survey,
you'll get a free T-shirt.

217
00:11:57,988 --> 00:11:59,865
We as attorneys support LGBTQIA+ rights.

218
00:11:59,949 --> 00:12:02,409
-Get a free T-shirt!
-Free T-shirts!

219
00:12:02,493 --> 00:12:04,119
Free T-shirt. Your signature.

220
00:12:04,203 --> 00:12:06,789
Geez, we're attorneys.
What are we doing here?

221
00:12:06,872 --> 00:12:10,626
One of the main jobs of pro bono attorneys
is supporting human rights groups.

222
00:12:11,544 --> 00:12:12,545
We're with you.

223
00:12:14,088 --> 00:12:15,673
Come get a T-shirt!

224
00:12:18,926 --> 00:12:20,886
Damn. This isn't working.

225
00:12:20,970 --> 00:12:22,805
-It's not working, is it?
-No, this won't do.

226
00:12:22,888 --> 00:12:25,766
-We shouldn't act like attorneys here.
-You're right.

227
00:12:25,849 --> 00:12:27,184
Yes. Let's get going.

228
00:12:27,726 --> 00:12:29,061
What?

229
00:12:29,937 --> 00:12:30,896
What is it?

230
00:12:31,981 --> 00:12:33,274
Follow us!

231
00:12:33,857 --> 00:12:34,817
Geez!

232
00:12:35,568 --> 00:12:37,236
-What is it?
-Nan-hui!

233
00:12:37,319 --> 00:12:39,989
GET A T-SHIRT BY DONATING
AND TAKING OUR SURVEY

234
00:12:40,072 --> 00:12:42,825
-Okay, come on out.
-Hey!

235
00:12:46,453 --> 00:12:48,455
I'm a public figure.
What if someone recognizes--

236
00:12:48,539 --> 00:12:51,250
If you're at a festival,
you should dress for the occasion.

237
00:12:51,333 --> 00:12:54,044
Occasion, my foot. You really think
people would come for this?

238
00:12:54,128 --> 00:12:55,671
Could we take a photo with you?

239
00:12:55,754 --> 00:12:57,172
Please, just one!

240
00:12:57,256 --> 00:12:58,257
-They came.
-I'll take it.

241
00:12:58,340 --> 00:13:00,884
-Thank you!
-Okay. One, two, three.

242
00:13:01,802 --> 00:13:02,970
You look so pretty!

243
00:13:03,053 --> 00:13:04,972
You're so beautiful.

244
00:13:05,055 --> 00:13:08,225
No, I'm a real manly man.

245
00:13:08,309 --> 00:13:09,560
Why am I speaking like this?

246
00:13:09,643 --> 00:13:11,353
-We'll root you. Good luck.
-Good luck.

247
00:13:11,437 --> 00:13:13,939
Excuse me, could you come over here
and sign your names?

248
00:13:14,023 --> 00:13:15,608
-Okay.
-Thank you.

249
00:13:15,691 --> 00:13:17,610
Sign here and take your T-shirts.

250
00:13:17,693 --> 00:13:18,861
Ms. Yoo, give me my pants.

251
00:13:18,944 --> 00:13:19,945
We want a photo too!

252
00:13:20,029 --> 00:13:21,405
Please take a photo with us!

253
00:13:21,488 --> 00:13:24,033
-Could you take it for us?
-Should I take it? Okay.

254
00:13:24,658 --> 00:13:25,784
Here we go. One, two, three.

255
00:13:26,744 --> 00:13:28,621
-Thank you. Now, stop.
-One, two, three. Great!

256
00:13:28,704 --> 00:13:29,997
-Ms. Yoo.
-Smile!

257
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,666
-Can't we take a few more, please?
-My goodness.

258
